<p class="">We are not sacking the soldiers. We need them, and need to use them in other places where they can be better used. I think the use and the moral value of these troops while Greece has been trying to establish her freedom have been very great.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
