<p class="">Would it not be advisable to wait until the winter, which may give opportunity for renewed sporadic outbreaks by the bandits, is more advanced before my right hon. Friend decides to withdraw the troops? Will he, in all circumstances, keep there the relatively small British Mission which has served Greece so well?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
