<p class="">No, it has not been taken. It will come before the Cabinet at an early date, and the whole thing will be gone into. I repeat that there are two separate subjects here. One is the matter of the Mission, about which the hon. Member for the Combined English Universities (Mr. K. Lindsay) asked me, and the other is the question of the troops. We shall come to our decision in due course, and announce it.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
